'''Acayucan''' is a city in the [[Mexican state]] of [[Veracruz]], located in the state's southeast, in the [[Olmeca (region)|Olmeca]] region. It serves as the municipal seat for the [[Acayucan Municipality]].
At the 2005 INEGI Census, Acayucan reported a population of 49,945.<ref>{{cite web|title=Acayucan |url=http://www.e-local.gob.mx/work/templates/enciclo/veracruz/municipios/30003a.htm |work=Enciclopedia de los Municipios de México |publisher=[[Instituto Nacional para el Federalismo y el Desarrollo Municipal]] |accessdate=8 November 2008 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070523100119/http://www.e-local.gob.mx/work/templates/enciclo/veracruz/municipios/30003a.htm |archivedate=23 May 2007 }}</ref>
